    IncrementalMountExtensionInput  
    IncrementalMountRenderCoreExtension.InputProvider<R extends Node.LayoutResult<?>>
    The provider that client frameworks must set on IncrementalMountRenderCoreExtension to enable the extension to collect the required data from the Node.LayoutResult during the layout pass.
